*pythia-8.2.09-r1 (05 Jun 2015)

  05 Jun 2015; Andrew Savchenko <bircoph@gentoo.org> +pythia-8.2.09-r1.ebuild,
  +files/pythia8209-root-noninteractive.patch,
  +files/pythia8209-run-tests.patch, metadata.xml:
  Version bump. Add new deps. Fix tests, they can be run in parallel
  now using standard emake. Imported from the science overlay.

